  <Strings>
    <Section>Main</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>268572</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_260_070_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>バンディ将軍、
あの子も養子候補ですか</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>General Bandi, that child may be
a suitable candidate for adoption.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>268676</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_260_070_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ああ……親も探してはみたが、
見つからなかった</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I realize that... Despite the search, no
traces of her parents were found.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>268872</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_260_070_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>近頃、生活に困窮し
子どもを捨てる親が
増えています</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>More and more parents living in poverty
choose to abandon their kids.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>268872</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_260_070_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>いくら呼びかけても
向こうは捨てたわけですから
名乗り出るわけありません</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>No matter how much they cry out,
the parents won't take them back
once their decision is made.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>268984</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_260_070_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>これもすべて……
長引く戦争で
民が飢えているせいか……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>This is the result of a starving nation
in the midst of a drawn-out war...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
